            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Workaround (assuming no args passed to `nvim` in the cmd line. Have not tested otherwise):\n\n```lua\n-- Run this in user config\nvim.api.nvim_create_autocmd(\"UIEnter\", {\n    group = vim.api.nvim_create_augroup(\"start-ui2\", {}),\n    once = true,\n    callback = function()\n        require(\"vim._core.ui2\").enable({ enable = true })\n    end,\n})\n```",
            "created_at": "2026-03-30T00:07:49Z",
